# Survey Engine MVP — Phased Implementation Action Plan

> **Stack:** Spring Boot 4.0.3 · Java 25 · Gradle · PostgreSQL · Flyway · Redis · RabbitMQ  
> **SRS Reference:** [survey-engine-mvp-srs.md](file:///home/amnayem/Projects/personal/Survey-Engine/docs/survey-engine-mvp-srs.md)

