## Project State Summary

| Aspect | Status |
|---|---|
| Bootstrap class | ✅ [SurveyEngineApplication.java](file:///home/amnayem/Projects/personal/Survey-Engine/src/main/java/com/bracits/surveyengine/SurveyEngineApplication.java) |
| Build config | ✅ Gradle with all infra deps (JPA, Flyway, Redis, RabbitMQ, Security/OAuth2, Actuator, OTel) |
